Package: BOSSS
Title: Bayesian Optimisation for Simulation-based Sample Size
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Duncan",
           family = "Wilson",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "d.t.wilson@leeds.ac.uk",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: An interactive app and package for solving sample size 
    determination problems for clinical trials with multiple design
    parameters, and where power (or other constraints / objectives) 
    has to be estimated using simulation.
